snippet.title: Need For Speed: Most Wanted (2005) | Mobile/java
snippet.description:
Full Walkthrough (worst emulation music in-game menu)

Info:
Genre: Racing
Release date: 2006
Developer: Firemint
Platform: Java (J2me)
Official site - https://web.archive.org/web/20070311072851/http://www.firemint.com:80/nfsmw.htm

About this game:
Need for Speed Most Wanted is a racing game based on the underground tuner car culture. Win the races in story mode to earn money for performance and visual upgrades to your cars. Replay previously completed races using the quick play option. The ultimate goal is to complete all races and create the fastest, coolest car possible!
